Aamadu Salif KEBE, koroowo (commissaire), ardiiɗo salndu Département Juridique et Contentieux ndun toɗɗaama hunndukoojo (porte parole) CENI on fii woote hooreejo leydi ndin 11 Oktoombur 2015.
Ndee fewjoore waɗnde ñannde 20 Suwiyee 2015 laɓɓinirii ligge makko ɗen nii :
- Newnugol jokkondiral hakkunde CENI on e jamaa heɗitiiɓe ɓe ɓen ;
- Wonugol ruttorde hertinornde hakkunde CENI on e Jaayɗe (médias) ɗen ;
- Okkugol CENI on lomntal moƴƴal ka kewuuji (événements) yaasi ;
- Hoynugol no kumpite CENI ɗen yaajira ;
- Townugol fii CENI on wowtina hakkunde makko e jamaa on.
En maandinay wonde CENI on hino mofti calɗi 11 jeyaa e majji salndu kabaaru e jokkondiral (communication et information) ndun.
Hara pooɗondiral waɗoyay ko yowitii e mbaawka ?
